title: Schile Imbiss and Lebensmittel
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Pizza, International, Italian, Buffet, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Turkish snack bar offering a wide variety of unique vegetarian and vegan dishes. In addition to traditional favorites like falafel, fava bean dip, and lentil salad, this Mediterranean restaurant offers a vegetarian pizza with a vegan alternative.
